  <p class="margin"> <h1 style="color:#222222; background:#FFFFFF;"><u>Tanker Ship</u>- <em>Tanker ships are made to carry large amounts of liquid cargo.
  Aside from oil, some tankers also transport chemicals, water, and even wine. There are different sizes of these ships.
  Some have a liquid capacity of hundreds of thousands of tons.</p></em> </h1>
  </body>
